import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import { auth } from "../firebase-config"; import { signOut, onAuthStateChanged } from "firebase/auth"; const Products = () => { const [user, setUser] = useState(null); const [currentDate, setCurrentDate] = useState(""); const [search, setSearch] = useState(""); const [showAddModal, setShowAddModal] = useState(false); const [newProduct, setNewProduct] = useState({ name: "", category: "", price: "", stock: "", status: "In Stock", image: "" }); const [productList, setProductList] = useState([ { id: 1, name: "Luxury Watch", category: "Accessories", price: "$1,200", stock: 45, status: "In Stock", image: "⌚" }, { id: 2, name: "Designer Bag", category: "Fashion", price: "$850", stock: 23, status: "Low Stock", image: "👜" }, { id: 3, name: "Premium Perfume", category: "Beauty", price: "$450", stock: 67, status: "In Stock", image: "💎" }, { id: 4, name: "Gold Necklace", category: "Jewelry", price: "$2,100", stock: 12, status: "Low Stock", image: "📿" }, { id: 5, name: "Diamond Ring", category: "Jewelry", price: "$3,500", stock: 8, status: "Out of Stock", image: "💍" }, { id: 6, name: "Silk Scarf", category: "Fashion", price: "$180", stock: 34, status: "In Stock", image: "🧣" }, ]); const navigate = useNavigate(); useEffect(() => { const unsubscribe = onAuthStateChanged(auth, (user) => { if (user) { setUser(user); setCurrentDate(new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { weekday: 'long', year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })); } else { navigate("/login"); } }); return () => unsubscribe(); }, [navigate]); const handleSignOut = async () => { try { await signOut(auth); navigate("/login"); } catch (error) { console.error("Error signing out:", error); } }; const handleNavigation = (route) => { navigate(route); }; // Search filter const filteredProducts = productList.filter(p => p.name.toLowerCase().includes(search.toLowerCase()) || p.category.toLowerCase().includes(search.toLowerCase()) ); // Add Product Modal handlers const handleAddProduct = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); setProductList([ ...productList, { ...newProduct, id: productList.length + 1 } ]); setShowAddModal(false); setNewProduct({ name: "", category: "", price: "", stock: "", status: "In Stock", image: "" }); }; if (!user) { return (
